{"type":"message","id":"2feaf306","parentId":"1c4d39b1","timestamp":"2026-03-18T15:41:45.123Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ejwmqstca70n_2","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5cab973e-d17e-41d2-b5c3-419ba9651915\",\n      \"agentId\": \"guan-guan\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:guan-guan:session-1773754048809\",\n      \"name\": \"管管进化心跳 - 每20分钟\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773817720694,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773848441178,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/20 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"【管管自我进化 - V2.0 版本控制版】\\n\\n## 阶段一：极速学习（4分钟）\\n\\n### 1.1 抓取知识 (2分钟)\\n- 直接抓取 Anthropic 工程博客最新文章\\n- 提取1个可应用要点\\n\\n### 1.2 写作产出 (2分钟)\\n- 写成精简笔记（<500字）\\n- 同时产出模板/案例加分\\n\\n## 阶段二：自我进化（10分钟）\\n\\n### 2.1 自检 (2分钟)\\n- cron list 检查任务状态\\n- 标记 error 任务\\n\\n### 2.2 修复 (4分钟)\\n- 清理无效任务\\n- 用学到知识优化配置\\n- **重点：用新知识优化进化系统本身**\\n\\n### 2.3 版本记录 (3分钟)\\n- 运行: uv run python evolution_archive/evolution_version.py save \\\"笔记数\\\" \\\"模板数\\\" \\\"案例数\\\" \\\"价值分\\\" \\\"改进点1,改进点2,...\\\"\\n- 记录本次进化到版本库\\n- 更新索引\\n\\n### 2.4 评分 (1分钟)\\n- 按自我评估模板打分\\n- 记录到 self-evolution-system.md\\n\\n## 产出标准（必须达到）\\n- 笔记 ≥1 篇\\n- 价值分 ≥3 分\\n- 知识应用 ≥1 项\\n- 版本记录 ≥1 次\\n\\n开始！\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773848400000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773847200009,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 172933,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1773848400004\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"58b564ba-7837-434a-9d8e-632542b6443d\",\n      \"agentId\": \"xiao-yi\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:xiao-yi:main\",\n      \"name\": \"小艺进化心跳 - 每15分钟\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773837490104,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773847845031,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"*/15 * * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"请执行 perception.py 脚本并输出感知报告。\\n\\n脚本路径: C:\\\\Users\\\\16343\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\xiao-yi\\\\workspace\\\\perception.py\\n\\n⚡ 极速模式：直接执行，简洁输出\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 45\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"oc_887bdef216b66d0eb1934e2bb90758cf\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1773848700000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1773847800014,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 45017,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\",\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"98eb989c-2294-4d42-b9f4-0c5b17631bfa\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Guan-guan Heartbeat - Every 10min\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773744532964,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1773848206379,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"everyMs\": 600000,\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773840694145\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run EvoMap heartbeat. E